---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="PHCDevworks"
  description="Design systems, UI tooling, and developer infrastructure. Open source. Built for developers."
>
  <section style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 5rem 2rem;">
    <article style="margin-bottom: 6rem;">
      <h1
        class="brand"
        style="font-size: clamp(3rem, 10vw, 7rem); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 2rem;"
      >
        PHCDEVWORKS
      </h1>
      <p
        style="font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); line-height: 1.3; margin-bottom: 2rem; max-width: 900px;"
      >
        We build design systems, UI tooling, and developer infrastructure.
      </p>
      <p
        class="muted-text"
        style="font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 700px;"
      >
        Everything is open source. Everything is on GitHub.
      </p>
    </article>

    <article class="divider" style="padding-top: 4rem; margin-bottom: 6rem;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; font-weight: 800;">
        Projects
      </h2>

      <div style="display: grid; gap: 3rem;">
        <div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
            <a
              href="https://github.com/phcdevworks/spectre-tokens"
              class="link"
            >
              Spectre Tokens
            </a>
          </h3>
          <p class="muted-text" style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.7;">
            Design tokens that define the visual language. JSON, JS/TS, CSS
            variables, and Tailwind outputs. One source of truth for every
            surface.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
            <a href="https://github.com/phcdevworks/spectre-ui" class="link">
              Spectre UI
            </a>
          </h3>
          <p class="muted-text" style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.7;">
            Core styling layer. Consumes tokens, ships CSS. Base styles,
            components, utilities, and recipe helpers. No framework lock-in.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
            <a
              href="https://github.com/phcdevworks/spectre-ui-astro"
              class="link"
            >
              Spectre UI Astro
            </a>
          </h3>
          <p class="muted-text" style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.7;">
            Astro integration. Typed components that map to Spectre UI classes.
            No duplicated logic. No style bloat.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
            <a href="https://github.com/phcdevworks/spectre-icons" class="link">
              Spectre Icons
            </a>
          </h3>
          <p class="muted-text" style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.7;">
            Icon system tuned to Spectre spacing, stroke, and typography scales.
            Product-ready, no fuss.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="divider" style="padding-top: 4rem; margin-bottom: 6rem;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; font-weight: 800;">
        Philosophy
      </h2>
      <div
        style="display: grid; gap: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.7; max-width: 800px;"
      >
        <p>Design tokens once. Use everywhere. No copy-paste. No drift.</p>
        <p>
          CSS that consumes tokens. Components that consume CSS. Clean layers.
          Clear dependencies.
        </p>
        <p>
          Open source. No vendor lock. Build what you need. Modify what you
          want.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="divider" style="padding-top: 4rem; margin-bottom: 6rem;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; font-weight: 800;">
        Links
      </h2>
      <div>
        <p style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          <a href="https://github.com/phcdevworks" class="link">
            github.com/phcdevworks
          </a>
        </p>
        <p class="muted-text" style="font-size: 1.125rem;">
          All repos. All docs. All roadmaps.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>

    <footer class="divider" style="padding-top: 3rem; padding-bottom: 3rem;">
      <p class="muted-text" style="font-size: 0.875rem;">Â© 2025 PHCDevworks</p>
    </footer>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
